I found a potentially more serious consistency question than the round-0 issues: I don’t see the orchestrator fetching newly-pushed `work/*` refs after startup, even though it now integrates from a private clone. I’m tracing that path end-to-end in the orchestrator loop before I finalize, because if there isn’t a fetch on the integrate path that would be a real blocker despite the passing smokes.
